data.description: Get your LOWER payment with a special interest rate 3-2-1 BUYdown! Charming home in Woodland Hills Village, just down the street from the Greenbelts, Parks, and pool. Spacious lot with large backyard, Outdoor grilling/kitchen area is great for entertaining. Birds & wildlife are regular visitors. Detached 2 car garage. Large living room with a custom fireplace mantle, island cooktop, updated appliances in the kitchen.  Recent paint, upgraded flooring throughout.  Energy Efficient Smart home with smart technology in place to control lights and thermostat, and so more. Low utility bill here! Remodeled master bathroom with walk-in shower. Zoned to excellent Humble ISD schools including greenbelt trails that lead to Woodland Hills Elementary and Kingwood Middle School. Quiet & established community In the front of Kingwood with Easy access to Hwy 59.  You've got to see this one TODAY.
